            <title>[LU-4778] Update catlog if some plain log is deleted during proecessing</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4778</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Plain log could be deleted if it becomes empty when processing catlog (see llog_cat_process()), however, we missed updating catlog and closing the destroyed plain log, that&apos;ll cause trouble when catlog close (llog_cat_close()) trying to destroy the empty plain log again.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
